# System Health

{% if issues %}

!!! warning "Flagged instruments"
    The list below includes microscopes that are **Offline** or in **Warning** state.

<div class="aic-grid" aria-label="Flagged instrument cards">
  {% for inst in issues %}
  <div class="aic-card">
    <div class="aic-card__body">
      <div class="aic-card__title" markdown="span">
        [{{ inst.display_name }}](instruments/{{ inst.id }}/)
        <span class="aic-chip aic-chip--status aic-chip--{{ inst.status.color }}" title="{{ inst.status.reason }}">{{ inst.status.badge }}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="aic-muted" style="margin: .2rem 0 .65rem;" markdown="span">
        {{ inst.manufacturer | default('—', true) }}{% if inst.model %} · {{ inst.model }}{% endif %}
      </div>

      <div markdown="span">
        **Why:** {{ inst.status.reason | default('—', true) }}
      </div>

      <div class="aic-kv" style="margin-top: .55rem;">
        <div>Last QC</div><div>{{ inst.status.last_qc_date | default('—', true) }}</div>
        <div>Last maint.</div><div>{{ inst.status.last_maint_date | default('—', true) }}</div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: .85rem;" markdown="span">
        [Open history](instruments/{{ inst.id }}/history.md){ .md-button }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

{% else %}

!!! success "No active issues"
    All instruments are currently healthy.

{% endif %}
